	(text "Display:\n- LED Matrix HUB 75 32x64\n\nMicrocontroller:\n- ESP-S3-DevKitC-1\n\nAudio:\n- MAX98357A I2S 3W Mono Amplifier Class D Filterless Amplifier Breakout Module\n- GERUI DFplayer Mini 3 Watt 8 Ohm Speaker with JST-PH2.0 mm Pin\n\nLight Sensor\n- GY-302 BH1750 BH1750FVI\n\nRotary Encoder\n- Taiss Rotary Encoder Module KY-040 360\n\nPower Supply:\n- Rectifier 5V, 5A, Meanwell RS-25-5\n- Cable: IEC C13 Power Cord with CEE 7/7 (Schuko) Plug\n- Connector: IEC 60320 C14 panel-mount inlet with integrated rocker switch and fuse holder\n- Fuse: T1AL / T1AH 250 V, 5×20 mm"
